    "body": "Meanwhile `eth.getBlock('latest')` is returning the correct block again. Looking at the log I am realizing that Nethermind was reporting that a new block was discovered, but not that it was processed. Nethermind only started processing the blocks again 8.5 hours later. \r\n[nethermind_continued.log](https://github.com/NethermindEth/nethermind/files/9290448/nethermind_continued.log)\r\n\r\n",
